latestIgtvVideos.caption:
First Impressions. 

@loiscosmetics Meet me in the Underworld Palette. 

I wanted to film how this palette performed on initial use just because I have missed 3 restocks of this palette. I wanted to know if I waited for something good. BUT do you see this look!?
From the shades that I used it performed 10|10. The shimmers are my preferred formula, high impact but not that jelly/ mushy texture. The mattes blend like a dream. If you like this colour story. Get it on restock 100%

latestIgtvVideos.title: Sunset Cut - Crease.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The @madebymitchell Head in the Clouds palette really is that palette!! Can you tell me that all the looks ive done with it are the same?? I cant! 

Really wanted to use the pinks in the palette and it turned into a sunset sorta vibe and I loved it! This look was filmed late at night so im sorry about the lighting. This year I really am going to invest in more lights 👌🏻

My lashes are @tatti_lashes but I forgot which style sorry! They are my fave brands for lashes at the moment! 

The liner is the Tattoo Liner by @kvdveganbeauty 💓

latestIgtvVideos.title: Poise Collections Story Takeover.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Did a story takeover for @poise.collections using a full face of their brushes. 
They are synthetic and non shedding. 
I highly recommend them as they are also super soft. If you live in Wales and would like to support a small welsh business Id urge you to check them out! 
Hope you like it. 

I used the @bperfectcosmetics  x @staceymariemua Carnival 3 Love Tahiti Palette. 
@plouise_makeup_academy @plouise1 Black canvas and Crisp Finish paint in Sweet and sour. As well as Rumour Base 2 to prime the whole eye. 
@peachesmakeup Snakebite Pigment all over the lid! ( isnt it gorgeous!)
